      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874487,
      "updated": 1772874487
    },
    {
      "id": "69abeaef5b4c472e2155ad8f",
      "text": "[ソシオニクス]における[論理と倫理]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874484,
      "updated": 1772878635
    },
    {
      "id": "69abeafd000000000078d571",
      "text": " 字面が紛らわしい",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874494,
      "updated": 1772874506
    },
    {
      "id": "69abeb07000000000078d573",
      "text": " [logic] – [ethic]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874504,
      "updated": 1772874519
    },
    {
      "id": "69abeaf3000000000078d564",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874484,
      "updated": 1772874484
    },
    {
      "id": "69abeb2f000000000078d574",
      "text": "from [「人間の相対性」]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874544,
      "updated": 1772874545
    },
    {
      "id": "69abeb35000000000078d576",
      "text": "https://casual-typology.blogspot.com/2024/01/dual-by-aushra-dichotomy03.html",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874550,
      "updated": 1772874550
    },
    {
      "id": "69abeaf3000000000078d565",
      "text": "[* 全ての倫理型]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874484,
      "updated": 1772874484
    },
    {
      "id": "69abeaf3000000000078d566",
      "text": "\t高感受性：自身と他者の感情状態の引き出し ([* E]) と倫理的感性・好き嫌い ([* R]) [line https://casual-typology.blogspot.com/2024/03/socionics-dual-nature-of-man.html#:~:text=%E8%87%AA%E5%88%86%E8%87%AA%E8%BA%AB%E3%81%A8%E4%BB%96%E3%81%AE%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%85%E3%81%AE%E6%84%9F%E6%83%85%E3%81%AB%E7%B2%BE%E9%80%9A%E3%81%97%E3%81%A6%E3%81%84%E3%81%BE%E3%81%99]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874484,
      "updated": 1772874484
    },
    {
      "id": "69abeaf3000000000078d567",
      "text": "\t\t[* R:] [\" 誰が誰を好きで、嫌いなのか、誰が誰のことをどう感じているのかという感情にも精通していますし、]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874484,
      "updated": 1772874484
    },
    {
      "id": "69abeaf3000000000078d568",
      "text": "\t\t[* E:] [\" 誰が今怒っているのか、悲しんでいるのか、楽しんでいるのかという感情にも精通しています]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874484,
      "updated": 1772874484
    },
    {
      "id": "69abeaf3000000000078d569",
      "text": "[* 全ての論理型]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874484,
      "updated": 1772874484
    },
    {
      "id": "69abeaf3000000000078d56a",
      "text": "\t低感受性：〈感情〉に属する情報信号の送受信をほとんど意識的に行っていない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874484,
      "updated": 1772874484
    },
    {
      "id": "69abeaf3000000000078d56b",
      "text": "\t\t> 論理的な人々の感情はすべて排除され、黙殺されています。言い換えると、論理タイプの感情にはほとんど無意識で、意識的なコントロールの影響を受けません。",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874484,
      "updated": 1772874484
    },
    {
      "id": "69abeaf3000000000078d56c",
      "text": "\t\tこの箇所の翻訳には難がある",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874484,
      "updated": 1772874484
    },
    {
      "id": "69abeaf3000000000078d56d",
      "text": "  > 論理的な人々が自分が愛されていると信じたがらないのと同じように、",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874484,
      "updated": 1772874484
    },
    {
      "id": "69abeaf3000000000078d56e",
      "text": "  \t愛情の共有は〈倫理〉IEに分類される",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874484,
      "updated": 1772874484
    },
    {
      "id": "69abeaf3000000000078d56f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874484,
      "updated": 1772874484
    }
  ]
}